---
description: Monorepo package manager and layout for board-games
globs: **/*
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use **Bun** (`bun install`, `bun run`, `bunx`) at the repo root. Do not use pnpm or npm for this project.
- Workspaces: `apps/*` and `packages/*` only. Web app is `apps/web` (package name `web`); Expo app is `apps/native` (package name `native`).
- Shared TypeScript bases live in `@board-games/config` (`packages/config`). Env validation for Next.js is in `@board-games/env` (`packages/env`, import `@board-games/env/web`).
- Stack-specific agent guidance also lives under `.agents/skills/` (copied from the next-example pattern).

See [CLAUDE.md](CLAUDE.md) for commands and conventions. UI primitives use Base UI via `@board-games/ui` (not Radix); see `.cursor/rules/base-ui-primitives.mdc` and `.agents/skills/base-ui-primitives/SKILL.md`.
